<hymn_number>77</hymn_number>
<title>Aw Kalvari!</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Kawlva banga len thiem hi leng aw,
 Ka Lal thihna mun va fang ka ting;
 Ziechun ei tatna va mung ka ting,
 A mela thisan kai neuno chu,
 Hehpih silhpuon nemin va thiek ka.

[V2]
 Aw Kalvari, aw Kalvari,
 Na chunga na lal kikhaikang kha;
 Tho in a kilhdennau thik bawt in,
 A thisan luong chu va thiek hul in.

[V3]
 2. Aw Kidron lui nang le tho inla,
 Na Lalpa dangchak vandawn sakin;
 Zu thukin A dangchak hai puona,
 Chiehin, A muk thiengtho nuoi akhun,
 Thieng dam dii-diei chan va luon sakin.

[V4]
 3. Kei ei ngaia dangchak hile chu,
 &quot;Aw, Kidron!&quot; tin ei hun sam intin;
 Atung laikhan va dawnsak tangka,
 Nang hun ngaia dangchak ahi ie,
 Chieh in thagau tui va dawn sakin.

[V5]
 4. Va chieh lengle bang ka va lawh dem,
 I Lalpau dangchak suhai dingin?
 Theihna bangmah ka nei puoh hi uo!
 Chieh chu chieh ingka Kalvari-ah,
 A thisan luong bek va thiek ingka.

[V6]
 5. Kalvari leh aw Jerusalem,
 Ka Lal nunnem hi ei sunpih un;
 I gitloh zieka liem thuok ahi,
 Tho unla kap in ban zak hitiu,
 Van Belam No tha a kiek ni hin.</lyrics>
</song>